name: Australia
description:
A unique 12” up cycled retro LP vinyl with hand made and cut stencil designed and created by Tuvsday.

This exciting one of a kind stencil artwork is a great gift idea for you or your loved ones. It adds a unique and interesting touch to your home or office space.

Ready to hang or easily framed and works great as part of a set.

Comes fully packaged for gift and safe postage.

Commissions and special request from photos:
Tuvsday can turn your photos into a stencil artwork. All you need to do is send in a photo and we will get back to you with a reply email and a quote that is based on your personal needs. Find out more at:

http://www.tuvsday.com

For any further information email: create@tuvsday.com
